Sign titles: notice - Headquarters Western Defense Command and Fourth Army. Western Defense Command and Fourth Army Wartime Civil Control Administration - Instructions to All Japanese Living on Bainbridge Island.

Handwritten on negative: Bainbridge Jap eviction.

Caption from March 25, 1942 Seattle Post-Intelligencer.

Date photograph was filed at the Seattle Post-Intelligencer (date of photograph and file date may differ by a month or more): March 25, 1942.
